01:28:03,113 --> 01:28:04,153
[SPEAKER_10]: I muted myself.

1129
01:28:04,314 --> 01:28:05,214
[SPEAKER_10]: That's okay.

1130
01:28:06,215 --> 01:28:06,555
[SPEAKER_10]: Aubrey?

1131
01:28:07,156 --> 01:28:07,536
[SPEAKER_10]: I'm yes.

1132
01:28:08,477 --> 01:28:09,197
[SPEAKER_10]: Yes, okay.

1133
01:28:09,377 --> 01:28:09,677
[SPEAKER_03]: Jean?

1134
01:28:09,697 --> 01:28:14,101
[SPEAKER_03]: I'm yes, despite my concerns.

1135
01:28:14,121 --> 01:28:14,921
[SPEAKER_03]: Okay.

