[SPEAKER_10]: Does anybody have any thoughts?

1159
01:29:27,674 --> 01:29:32,299
[SPEAKER_07]: I thought we just pass on it and carry on with the rest of the agenda and circle back.

1160
01:29:32,359 --> 01:29:36,903
[SPEAKER_07]: I think that one's, you know, deserves it.

1161
01:29:37,403 --> 01:29:38,604
[SPEAKER_07]: We start next time.

1162
