[SPEAKER_10]: Paulette, were you going to say something?

1164
01:29:43,929 --> 01:29:45,131
[SPEAKER_02]: No, well, actually, I'll carry on.

1165
01:29:45,591 --> 01:29:47,453
[SPEAKER_02]: I'll discuss it under the school committee.

1166
01:29:48,430 --> 01:29:55,736
[SPEAKER_10]: Okay, all right, so we'll save that one, and now we'll, oh, next is the school committee subcommittee check.

1167
