[SPEAKER_03]: Yes, there is with NPS parents and staff.

1173
01:30:30,012 --> 01:30:31,693
[SPEAKER_03]: Yeah.

1174
01:30:31,733 --> 01:30:39,075
[SPEAKER_12]: Paulette, is there a possibility that we could change that January 11th date?

1175
01:30:39,135 --> 01:30:43,376
[SPEAKER_12]: I have a school thing that came up and it'll be a conflict for me.

1176
01:30:43,776 --> 01:30:43,956
[SPEAKER_02]: Right.

1177
01:30:44,016 --> 01:30:45,937
[SPEAKER_02]: So I'm suggesting that we change January 11th.

1178
01:30:47,074 --> 01:30:47,514
