1407
01:47:47,023 --> 01:47:49,944
[SPEAKER_05]: And they've done an incredible job getting us all together.

1408
01:47:50,044 --> 01:47:55,447
[SPEAKER_05]: But as this ship sails in this big ocean, there's a lot of stuff that we have to still accomplish.

1409
01:47:55,947 --> 01:47:58,448
[SPEAKER_05]: And the calendar doesn't stop.

1410
01:47:59,048 --> 01:48:13,370
[SPEAKER_05]: So what I would suggest, my suggestion is, it's kind of a fun suggestion, is that at our next meeting, each one of us take three minutes to talk about what they've seen in this group over the year and what's important to them as we get to that September moment.

1411
01:48:13,710 --> 01:48:20,872
[SPEAKER_05]: Because I fear that there are some major issues that we're just going to be, it's going to be August and we just haven't even talked about.

1412
